  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个飞地（enclave）的生命周期状态图。核心状态包括：FRESH、RUNNABLE、RUNNING、STOPPED，以及最终的DESTROYED。起点是sm_create_enclave创建飞地，终点是销毁后回到终止状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRESH",
        "RUNNABLE",
        "RUNNING",
        "STOPPED",
        "DESTROYED",
        "sm_create_enclave",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到RUNNABLE和RUNNING之间是双向的吗？还是只能从RUNNABLE进入RUNNING？另外，STOPPED状态能直接回到RUNNING吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RUNNABLE",
        "RUNNING",
        "STOPPED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "RUNNABLE通过sm_run_enclave进入RUNNING；RUNNING正常退出可以回到RUNNABLE。STOPPED可以通过sm_resume_enclave恢复为RUNNING。另外，STOPPED、RUNNABLE、RUNNING这三个状态都能直接销毁到DESTROYED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RUNNABLE",
        "RUNNING",
        "STOPPED",
        "DESTROYED",
        "sm_run_enclave",
        "正常退出",
        "sm_resume_enclave",
        "sm_destroy_enclave"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主体框架：起点到FRESH是sm_create_enclave，FRESH到RUNNABLE标注\"初始化完成\"，然后RUNNABLE和RUNNING之间双向，RUNNING分出STOPPED，三个状态都连到DESTROYED，最后DESTROYED回到终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "FRESH",
        "RUNNABLE",
        "RUNNING",
        "STOPPED",
        "DESTROYED",
        "初始化完成"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，FRESH到RUNNABLE的转换条件我写的是\"初始化完成\"，但其他转换都是sm_开头的系统调用。这样混用会不会不一致？要不把FRESH到RUNNABLE的也改成sm_风格？不过\"初始化完成\"是内部事件，不是外部调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRESH",
        "RUNNABLE",
        "初始化完成"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我觉得保留\"初始化完成\"更真实，因为这一步是内部状态变更，不像sm_create_enclave、sm_run_enclave这些是用户显式调用的接口。这样区分内外部事件其实更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRESH",
        "RUNNABLE",
        "初始化完成",
        "sm_create_enclave",
        "sm_run_enclave"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以。那再确认一下销毁路径：RUNNABLE、RUNNING、STOPPED都要能直接到DESTROYED，触发条件都是sm_destroy_enclave。DESTROYED之后直接到终止状态，不需要额外标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RUNNABLE",
        "RUNNING",
        "STOPPED",
        "DESTROYED",
        "sm_destroy_enclave",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。状态图已按stateDiagram-v2语法绘制，包含所有状态和转换：起点→FRESH→RUNNABLE↔RUNNING↔STOPPED，以及三条销毁路径汇聚到DESTROYED→终点。标注了内部事件\"初始化完成\"和\"正常退出\"，其余为系统调用。",
